nother layer of aubergine and courgette slices over lentils then cover with remaining lentils. Sprinkle with cheese."},{"content":"Bake for 30-35 minutes (160°C) until golden. Remove from oven and allow to stand for a few minutes before serving."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Grate your own vegan cheese by placing pieces in mixing bowl and grating <b>5 sec\/speed 4<b>.","Tinned tomatoes can also be used instead of fresh ones. Omit step 1 and continue as per recipe.","Vegan cheese can be purchased at health food stores or from large supermarkets."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 10m","6 portions"]}